N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 218-7.1 - Applicability

State Regulations

This Subpart applies to all aftermarket parts that are
sold, offered for sale, or advertised for sale or use on 1993, 1994, 1996 and
subsequent model-year vehicles which are subject to New York State or Federal
emission standards. Notes
